#fasta_from_catalog
#This program creates a fasta file based on a list of RAD loci and the RAD catalog file from Stacks


//Required information: 
//(1) Stacks batch_x.catalog.tags.tsv file
//(2) file with a list of RAD loci

//Output:
//One file with the sequences of the selected RAD loci. Default name is output.fasta.

//Usage:
//./fasta_from_catalog
//-c: Stacks catalog file, including path (default: batch_1.catalog.tags.tsv)
//-l: List of RAD tag Locus IDs to select (including path)
//-o: output file name (including path). Default: output.fasta
//-h: Prints this message
//no arguments: interactive mode